<section class="aboutus-sec">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="row patient-care-box-area about-content-area">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <h3>All about Talk To Treat</h3>
                        <p>
                            Over a period of time India has become one of the top most destination for medical tourism. It is all cause of the affordable medical coverage and best doctor panel(s) that India has to offer at just one tenth of the price that it might be availed at any other part of the world. In India, there is a plethora of the range of treatment and procedural options, the best quality of therapy and best medical infrastructure and skilled manpower to perform and with zero wait time, and beyond that the advantages can be enlisted endlessly when India is considered as a medical destination. But with great advantages comes some challenges too like,
                        </p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>How to choose the right doctor?</li>
                            <li>How to choose the right place for the treatment?</li>
                            <li>How to get the VISA and related permission?</li>
                            <li>How and when to travel?</li>
                            <li>Where to accommodate?</li>
                            <li>How to manage the pre and post treatment services?</li>

                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            The answer to all the questions is “Talk to Treat”!! A one stop solution for all the medical needs in India. When a patient starts sourcing for the different aspects of their medical travel, they face a lot of confusion and trickery financially. With “Talk to Treat” the patients are able to source the right Doctor, hospital and other facilities on the basis of real time reviews and experiences shared by other patients.
                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

